import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { LoginService } from 'src/app/service/login.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-home', templateUrl: './home.component.html', styleUrls: ['./home.component.css'], }) export class HomeComponent { isLogin: boolean = false; constructor(private login: LoginService, private router: Router) {} ngOnInit() { this.login.isSignedIn$.subscribe((status) => { this.isLogin = status; if (this.isLogin == false) { // this.router.navigate(['/logIn']); } }); } }
